<p><strong>We are  looking for passionate new PhD students, Master students, and undergraduates to join the team!</strong></p>

<h2 id="sponsorship-collaboration-and-partnership">Sponsorship, Collaboration, and Partnership</h2>
<p>The research and educational activities of HRG are supported by a diverse collection of government, industry, and academic partners along with a number of scholarship and fellowship programs. We continually strive to be the best stewards of this support any encourage any party interested in teaming with HRG to please contact <a href="mailto:ghuff@psu.edu">Prof. Huff</a>.</p>

